Name: Divine Flesh
FlavourText: Give up your flesh unto the gods, and in vulnerability find strength.

Name: Eternal Youth
FlavourText: Burn the spirit to vitalise the flesh.

Name: Immortal Ambition
FlavourText: You may live forever, so long as someone remains to be sacrificed.

Name: Corrupted Soul
FlavourText: As true belief fades, the facade of faith grows, leaving you powerful but hollow.

Name: Strength of Blood
FlavourText: Wreathed in madness and blood, you are unstoppable.

Name: Tempered by War
FlavourText: Tasalio and Valako test you, child of the volcano. Prove yourself worthy.

Name: Glancing Blows
FlavourText: Utter trust in your defence unleashes ultimate potential.

Name: Chainbreaker
FlavourText: No man may enslave you, for you have a secret: you're always angry.

Name: Wind Dancer
FlavourText:
Invite the enemy when you are strong, evade them when you are weak;
strike with the coming of the storm.

Name: The Traitor
FlavourText: The fewer there are, the less you have to share.

Name: Dance with Death
FlavourText: You circle the black scorpion with enmity, daring it time and again.

Name: Second Sight
FlavourText: Speak not, but listen, for danger reveals itself on the wind.

Name: The Agnostic
FlavourText: Put your faith in intellect rather than mysticism.

Name: Transcendence
FlavourText: Master the mortal world, and you may find immortality beyond.

Name: Inner Conviction
FlavourText: Your every move is calm and calculated with absolute certainty.

Name: Power of Purpose
FlavourText: Empowered by the divine, you fear no weapon of man.

Name: Supreme Decadence
FlavourText: You may find that having is less pleasing a thing than wanting.

Name: Supreme Grandstanding
FlavourText: Your fiery passion inspires everyone around you - especially your foes.

Name: Supreme Ego
FlavourText:
You are the heart of the empire, shining bright so that all are lifted up by your light.
Let none tell you otherwise.

Name: Supreme Ostentation
FlavourText:
Displays of power are not just for show. If you are never truly tested,
you may divert those resources elsewhere.
